To start, make a complete copy of the game install directory. Then delete half the mods and try it and see if it works. If it does, then you know the problem mod is in the one of the ones you deleted. If it still crashes repeat that again delete half of the remaining mods. Keep doing this until you've isolated which mod it is which is causing the problem.
